            <h2>About KhumaloCraft</h2>
            <p>KhumaloCraft is dedicated to bringing the finest artisan crafts from the heart of our local communities to the global stage. We believe in the power of craft to connect cultures, tell stories, and create a sustainable future for artisans around the world.</p>
            <p>Founded in 2024, KhumaloCraft has grown from a small local market to an international platform, showcasing a diverse range of handmade products from talented artisans. Our mission is to empower artisans by providing them with a global audience, while also making the world's rich tapestry of cultures accessible to everyone.</p>
            
            <h3>Our Mission</h3>
            <p>Our mission is to empower local artisans by connecting them with a global audience, ensuring that every purchase directly supports the craftsperson behind it. We strive to preserve traditional crafts and promote sustainable practices within the artisan community.</p>

            <h3>Our Vision</h3>
            <p>We envision a world where every artisan has the opportunity to thrive and where consumers can easily access and treasure authentic handmade goods. Through KhumaloCraft, we aim to build bridges between cultures and celebrate the beauty of diversity through craft.</p>
